#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.174:0.2"
msgid "14. Oghavagga "
msgstr "14. Floods "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.174:0.3"
msgid "174. Ganthasutta "
msgstr "174. Personal Ties "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.60, sc1
msgctxt "sn45.174:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, ganthā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four ties. "

msgctxt "sn45.174:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn45.174:1.3"
msgid "Abhijjhā kāyagantho, byāpādo kāyagantho, sīlabbataparāmāso kāyagantho, idaṃsaccābhiniveso kāyagantho—"
msgstr "The personal ties to covetousness, ill will, misapprehension of precepts and observances, and the insistence that this is the only truth. "

msgctxt "sn45.174:1.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro ganthā. "
msgstr "These are the four ties. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.174:1.5"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ ganthānaṃ abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya pahānāya … pe … ayaṃ ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvetabbo”ti. "
msgstr "The noble eightfold path should be developed for the direct knowledge, complete understanding, finishing, and giving up of these four ties.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.174:1.6"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

